  <abstract>Image of group of at least fifteen men in bathing suits standing on the edge of pier at Burlington Beach, near Brant Inn. Immediately behind them and on a raised platform are two Orthodox priests giving benedictions flanked by two men in Greek fustanella, holding flags. A crowd of onlookers surround the group.</abstract>
